data.description: Price reduced. Seller motivated. Welcome to Parkview At Lake Shore also known as Concorde Estates is a lovely “Energy Efficient” home with 4 spacious Bedroom; 1 Flex Room downstairs (can be an extra room, study, dining or anything you desire); 3.5 Bathroom; and Insulated 2 Car Garage that has a PORTABLE AC unit and BUILT-IN CABINETS that  which can be used to park cars, gym, or any other type of use.  This home is a true “Energy Efficient” powered home with SOLAR PANELS and TESLA BACKUP BATTERY (paid off) that distributes energy efficiently throughout the house providing tremendous financial savings. In addition it has SMART HOME gadgets, RING Camera system to ensure safety, WATER SOFTNER system that produces clean and pure water throughout the house guaranteeing a healthier and sustainable live style, two pation back and front for relaxation and large size FENCED back yard to build your dream backyard "Oasis".  The community offers Recreation Center, Pool, state-of-the-art Fitness Center, Tennis, Picnic Area, Dog Park, Beautiful walking trail, and more. Don't miss your chance to own this property and live here.
